{"tid":1322751,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"不得不吹奏前左膠吳志森令到好多和理非/中立派支持學生","createTime":"2019-07-16T04:43:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T05:28:54.000Z","uid":167971,"like":48,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ce0a4b4ab7aa2a97df642813a8a2df4b7c882063","tid":1322751,"uid":167971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T04:43:05.000Z","msg":"以前都好憎呢個老野左膠成日話人勇敢無用乜乜乜<br />\n自從送中之後佢開始轉駄幫番d後生仔講野<br />\nD片有理據得嚟又唔會偏激 <br />\n啱哂d和理非/勇武潔癖嘅人睇 <br />\n説服到d人唔再對學生反感 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我屋企兩老以前俾一百張長輩圖佢地都唔q明<br />\n一俾佢地睇呢個吳志森長輩嘅片第二日即刻轉駄<br />\n屌9番d黑警轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以話我地就咁連登仔同d老一輩分析係作用不大<br />\n要搵d差唔多年紀 同聲同氣嘅同佢地講先有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個老野值得吹奏 快d share俾d老野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係參考短片可以share俾你地身邊嘅老野/和理非睇:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Xq6DfpbOXyg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FXq6DfpbOXyg&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXrc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=6f1e5695\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Xq6DfpbOXyg</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/luQsBiBsGHY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FluQsBiBsGHY&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXrc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=d85d8e3c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/luQsBiBsGHY</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/qeBAqgUV07U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FqeBAqgUV07U&d=SZ2g%2FZg1uDubc4iNJejiXrc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=60353dc2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/qeBAqgUV07U</a>"},{"pid":"aa47b137ea53c346d4a6